      • calculateXOffset

        double calculateXOffset(BoundingBox other,
                        double xOffset)
        if instance and the argument bounding boxes overlap in the Y and Z dimensions, calculate the offset between them in the X dimension.
        Parameters:
        other - the other BoundingBox
        xOffset - the X offset
        Returns:
        xOffset if the bounding boxes do not overlap or if xOffset is closer to 0 then the calculated offset. Otherwise return the calculated offset.
